OL,5, Former Chancellor Nadhim Zahawi has    
OL,6, told the BBC he paid nearly #5m to     
OL,7, authorities to settle his tax affairs. 
OL,9,FMr Zahawi was sacked last year as Tory 
OL,10,FParty chairman after an ethics inquiry 
OL,11,Ffound he had failed to disclose that   
OL,12,FHMRC was investigating his taxes.      
OL,14,FHe was sorry for not being "more       
OL,15,Fexplicit" in his ministerial           
OL,16,Fdeclaration on the settlement, he told 
OL,17,Fthe Sunday with Laura Kuenssberg show. 
OL,19,FBut he insisted HMRC had found it was a
OL,20,Fnon-deliberate, "careless" mistake.    
